data.description: Introducing a charming 2-bedroom, 1-bath gem with a private garage, nestles across the street from a serene lake with a picturesque walking path. This 1080 sq ft residence offers a perfect blend of comfort and tranquility. Step inside to discover an inviting living space with ample natural light, a well-appointed kitchen, and cozy bedrooms. Enjoy morning coffee overlooking the beauty of Loon Lake with a connected garage to make this home convenient living at its finest. Don't miss the chance to call this haven home!
